description: A mobile eatery providing a diverse menu reflecting San Diego's historical culture through food. The first campus-run food truck on the West Coast!Grilled California Prawn Tacos on Homemade Tortillas served with Roasted Garlic Guacamole & Fire Roasted Tomatillo SalsaGrilled Skirt Steak or Chicken Tacos on Homemade Tortillas with Roasted Garlic Guacamole, Onions and choice of SalsaGrilled Veggie SandwichAND SO MUCH MORE!
name: Torero Tu Go
